Gordon Mohr wrote:

&gt;Sounds good.
&gt;
&gt;We could also use an ever-changing tag like &#39;current&#39; to point to
&gt;whichever releaseis recommended for outside users, and then give
&gt;CVS instructions that fetch &#39;current&#39;, whatever it is, correct?
